[A previous posting indicated that 3 CFIA testing centres were set up, but
it appears that only 2 are operating at the moment. The identity of the PPV
strain as a D strain is useful information. D-strain isolates are less
aggressive than other PPV strains, and they are not seed-transmitted. -Mod.DH
